{"type": "article", "id": 33442, "title": "这些“纸板”马克杯，需要你“小心轻放”｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-10-18T23:13:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 34057, "name": "Michael & George"}, {"id": 34058, "name": "CatastrophiCreations"}, {"id": 34062, "name": "Bilge Nur Saltik"}, {"id": 34075, "name": "Inigo Elizalde Rugs"}, {"id": 34059, "name": "Tim Kowalczyk"}, {"id": 34060, "name": "Kat Gilbert"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 75, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161018203419NZi3veQ9PalDr0WE.jpg", "contents": "<p class=\"\">          </p><p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Drew by Michael &amp; George</h3><p>          </p><p>看腻了中规中矩的灯具想要来点不一样的？澳大利亚设计师夫妇 <a href=\"http://www.michaelandgeorge.com/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\">Michael &amp; George</a> 最近推出了一款名为 Drew 的台灯，采用了人们熟悉的木制铅笔的造型。末端的橡皮就是光源所在，为了营造出像是被隐形的手提着的感觉，笔尖处内置了一个需要旋扭的零件与底座相连。这个固定后从外部无法察觉的细节，在黑色电线的配合下，还能在桌上摆出极具创意的图案。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1070583203/drew-the-pencil-lamp\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，早鸟价为 209 澳元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018153150Rqj61fTgirB8s3Zn.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563333\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018153150esR2QYCTlm6rE8IU.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.780882\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018153151jAdVPDFclKRZ8iS9.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"3.150000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610181531512ZdMglu4QxO3JkIw.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.367647\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><h3>Loud Objects by Bilge Nur Saltik</h3><p>          </p><p>在今年的伦敦设计节上，设计师 <a href=\"http://bilgenursaltik.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bilge Nur Saltik</a> 带来了一款打破常规的音响系列 <a href=\"http://bilgenursaltik.com/loud-objects/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Loud Objects</a>。Saltik 拒绝了常见的塑料与钢材，选用大理石搭配木板制作了这些音响。它们作为装饰能很好地融入环境当中，并且还能充当烛台、托盘以及花器的功能，低调而实用。在续航方面，每款都配备了一块可以充电的电池。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018160024gE8suje1nk6wzIJ7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018160024w7Nzj8OiWMIlfqPm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018160024aUIFQE5q8v3grlbt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018160024F3srW9IVPgZn6K08.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.657702\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018160024UunBNSfieFzWxo4D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.602689\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Mugs by Tim Kowalczyk</h3><p>          </p><p>你可别被这些马克杯的外观给误导了，由美国设计师 <a href=\"http://timsceramics.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tim Kowalczyk</a> 制作的这些杯子都是用货真价实的陶土烧制的。Kowalczyk 在那些被人们抛弃的物品当中发现了一种独特的美，借助容易塑形的陶土模仿出了旧纸板质感。有意思的是，你还能在杯子上看到一句“小心轻放”的提醒。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018153129fgsZyJr5lDdUkmpH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018153129aVxRPlpbHO95LBQC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610181531291J0e9ytgaRh5NGdT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018153128GKVCP0hS1MEeXqcx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018153128uUvNnEs6KekygLhT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Cat Mod by Catastrophic Creations</h3><p>          </p><p>还为买什么样的猫爬架犹豫不决的话，现在你还能考虑自己动手拼一个出来。美国品牌 <a href=\"https://www.catastrophicreations.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Catastrophi Creations</a> 专营为喵星人设计的家具，两位猫控设计师最近推出了一款模块化的猫爬架 Cat Mod。这套家具由木制墙面架、织布和抓柱构成，每个装上织布的架子能够承受住 80 磅（约合 72.6 斤）的重量，让猫咪能够在上面尽情玩耍。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/2109380202/the-cat-mod-modular-climbing-systems\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，早鸟价从 27 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018153118vOKy8HDJYz0hBF93.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018153117VAwxNcMnP2G9UT1h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018153118KBmXvE634gfl0oIx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610181531188yuBCAMFlQZzNPRt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><h3>Glitch by Inigo Elizalde Rugs</h3><p>恼人的电脑故障也可以变成设计师的灵感来源。来自纽约地毯工作室 <a href=\"https://inigoelizalderugs.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Inigo Elizalde Rugs</a> 的设计团队曾经历过一次因电涌触发的故障，屏幕上出现的奇异线条经过精心设计后变成了地毯系列 <a href=\"https://inigoelizalderugs.com/collections/glitch/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Glitch</a> 的式样，有着一种独特的科技美感。所有的地毯都采用来自尼泊尔的荨麻、仙人掌、竹子等纤维手工制成。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610182254104zlaPsN6CXpwm752.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.488333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018225410ADQLgwxGylhI6SvK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.495000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018225410od3OHgR9VDnkpZLJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.506667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018225410RBxVcmwMWTtCeA1k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018225411y4FwUSeHkEvP7pgC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.506667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018225411khnDNy87Bs0I1dPJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.501667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Regina Royale Jam by Kat Gilbert</h3><p>          </p><p>Regina Royale 是奥地利设计师 <a href=\"http://katharinagilbert.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kat Gilbert</a> 的母亲创立的果酱品牌，每年她都会用新鲜的杏子、樱桃等水果亲手制作果酱。为了让母亲和顾客能够快速地分辨出不同的口味，Gilbert 以果实形状等原料相关的元素为灵感设计了一套相当简洁的黑白图案以示区别。通过分成四格的标签，信息一览无余。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018153053FMaE38U5xLJ1AiWl.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018153053GodAwzuZ26eVqMJB.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018153052cwzvSNMsObI2dhCV.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018153052UBC8FOJIM4V3oP26.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018153052txNmrPQJBd0SOqC7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161018153052iOBN9Yn64oRpTwqC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}